name: zonos-elements-readme
description: Documentation for integrating zonos-elements, no porduction code.

scripts.version:major: pnpm version major -m 'Bump version %s' && pnpm push:tags
scripts.version:minor: pnpm version minor -m 'Bump version %s' && pnpm push:tags
